07 Jan 82  Bruce Lucas at CMU    Created ChangeLog.tty, README, CompileReDraw.CM, ListReDraw.CM.    Eliminated PrintFloat (can't find .BR or .BCPL file!); now prints height        to two decimal places.    Changed ec in font directory from 177b to 377b, for the sake of those        printers that look at it.    Called it version 2.2. (Version 2.1 was created by Lyle Ramshaw by        OEDITing the .RUN file for version 2.0 to implement the change from        177b to 377b mentioned above).